## UI Primitives

- Prefer using `Button`, `Input`, `Card`, `Modal`, `LoadingSpinner`, `SingleSelect`, `MultiSelect`.
- `Button` has variants: `primary` (default), `secondary`, `outline`.
- `Modal` supports sizes: `sm`, `md`, `lg`, `xl`, `large`. Prefer `xl` for wizards.
- `Icon` maps string names to Heroicons; extend `iconMap` in `Icon.tsx` to add new icons.
- Notifications: use `useToast()` from `components/ui/Toast`.
- Error handling: wrap top-level routes with `components/ui/ErrorBoundary` (already done in `App.tsx`).
